:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
:: ApiTest -- A program to test several aspects of the Odin32 API            ::
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

With the development of SWT for OS/2, which uses the Odin32 sub-system, the
need has risen to be able to test the functionality of Odin32 at a more direct
level. This is to determine if issues with SWT applications are caused at the
SWT-JNI layer or are caused by Odin32.
